1.Name: NewsAnchor
1.Dialogue: The strange robot, Mantle, has been destroyed by the quizzical Quincy.

2.Name: NewsAnchor
2.Dialogue: With the robot gone and Amourtia Prison obliterated, Quincy runs free.

3.Name: NewsAnchor
3.Dialogue: Despite this sad news, having the strange robot gone eliminates one of our worries. But what's next? Who knows.
